Another Great Raid with UB...
By Ursi
JANUARY 10, 2004
Thanks again, Universal Brotherhood.
Well, we set out to drop Aerdin Dar in PoV - he wasn't up. Terris Thule wasn't up- nor Xanamech, nor just about any other flag mob. So we said what the heck and killed some mini bosses in the BoT Towers. Best loot I have ever seen drop with least amount of death. Rock the heck on.
